{"tid":849732,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我認我種族歧視","createTime":"2018-10-06T02:28:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T06:39:01.000Z","uid":91771,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"40ca7b1ce5f1b796343a3ec86b63e6093bb6bae2","tid":849732,"uid":91771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T02:28:12.000Z","msg":"話說今日搭電車，落車時有對外藉情侶企咗喺落車位諗住等人落晒就上車，於是我指一指車尾，同佢地講the entrance&rsquo;s over there，然後佢地講聲thank you,我就落咗車<br />\n<br />\n落車之後諗返起前日我都係搭電車，有個支那婆一開落車門就打算衝上來塞住個落車位，我當時係屌咗出聲，屌你，喺車尾上車呀！見佢一臉茫然，我又補多句蝗語<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不懂車尾上車嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n無辦法<br />\n劣種是要屌的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c34b631621c6c74a8f520f5dc2e81b5faafd9d0","tid":849732,"uid":196077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T06:25:44.000Z","msg":"我歧視樓狗老母做雞做到街知巷聞"},{"pid":"53092d85ea716a6c58bb6a7615ebbbc9b0ead0dc","tid":849732,"uid":91771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c34b631621c6c74a8f520f5dc2e81b5faafd9d0","tid":849732,"uid":196077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T06:25:44.000Z","msg":"我歧視樓狗老母做雞做到街知巷聞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T06:38:11.000Z","msg":"支那種嬲豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7993e22f3799377e75afbf4c533b656095939ec","tid":849732,"uid":196077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53092d85ea716a6c58bb6a7615ebbbc9b0ead0dc","tid":849732,"uid":91771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c34b631621c6c74a8f520f5dc2e81b5faafd9d0","tid":849732,"uid":196077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T06:25:44.000Z","msg":"我歧視樓狗老母做雞做到街知巷聞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T06:38:11.000Z","msg":"支那種嬲豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj